et\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to use the Data &amp; More Compliance backend</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><h3>Introduction</h3>\n<p>The following is an introduction to the Data &amp; More Compliance server backend. There are 5 different functionality areas and a navigation bar to the left</p>\n<p>There are 3 key areas</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"595\" style=\"width: 621px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=621&amp;height=595&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png\" width=\"621\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=311&amp;height=298&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 311w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=621&amp;height=595&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 621w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=932&amp;height=893&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 932w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=1242&amp;height=1190&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 1242w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=1553&amp;height=1488&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 1553w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png?width=1863&amp;height=1785&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-38-14-4154-PM.png 1863w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\"></p>\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3>Navigation bar and high level areas</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-39-56-4268-PM.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<h3>Language setting</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-09-44-19-8102-PM.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Administrative Tools</h3>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"823\" style=\"width: 642px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=642&amp;height=823&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png\" width=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=321&amp;height=412&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 321w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=642&amp;height=823&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 642w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=963&amp;height=1235&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 963w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=1284&amp;height=1646&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 1284w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=1605&amp;height=2058&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 1605w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png?width=1926&amp;height=2469&amp;name=image-png-Aug-17-2023-10-13-50-7251-PM.png 1926w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\"></p>\n<p>See section on <a href=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/administrative-tools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">administrative tools</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
